headline: Lennar Corporation Declares Quarterly Dividends
summary: Lennar Corporation (NYSE: LEN and LEN.B), one of the nation's leading homebuilders, announced that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.50 per share for both Class A and Class B common stock payable on October 27, 2025 to holders of record at the close of business on October 10, 2025.

headline: The Haves And Have Nots
summary: On the surface, the U.S. economy appears strong, but both the economy and the market are being held up by a small number of actors. Read what investors need to know.
